c:["$","section",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-ink","children":"Security"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-2 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted","children":["$","p",null,{"children":"Access is gated by a single password (stored only as a hash) and a signed session cookie. Because the app is self-hosted, securing the host is your responsibility — run it behind HTTPS, keep the machine patched, and protect the database file and your environment variables (which hold secrets like your intervals.icu API key). No system is perfectly secure."}]}]]}]
